Subject: The first dropped valve seat

I was reading a Porsche biography last night and Ferry recounted the time when they were testing the first 3 VW prototypes and coming down the mountain, the head overcooled and the valve seat fell out. This was in 1938!

Overcooled sounds almost dreamy. :-)

